location_name: South Georgian Bay Regional Assessment Centre
PHU_fr: Bureau de santé publique du district de Simcoe-Muskoka
additional_information: Located in the back parking lot Royal Canadian Legion, so please use the Erie Street entrance, NOT the Ontario Street Entrance. There is no parking fee.  Please use the wait list app on www.gbfht.ca/cac or call to schedule an appointment
additional_information_fr: Situé dans la tente dans le stationnement de l’Équipe de Santé Familiale, à côté de l’hôpital.
